It muſt be owned, that the Courſe of this World is not ſteered according to ſuch Maxims, and that among the Profeſſors of Chriſtianity, there are but few who are found in the Exerciſe of a Self-denial perfectly conſiſtent herewith;
and the Diſtinction which our Lord himſelf made between the Children
Luke xvi 8. of this World, and the Children of Light, holds good to this Day.
